{"tid":1631520,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"呢場革命 不割先會贏","createTime":"2019-10-06T15:42:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T16:21:43.000Z","uid":56857,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"134c1a292d3e3ee3b20ab93215d5ebe0d0871567","tid":1631520,"uid":56857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:42:08.000Z","msg":"出面海量式話唔好破壞 <br />\n失民意 失外國支持<br />\n呢家到底係咩人破壞都唔撚知 <br />\n唔排除有狗有分破壞 屈手足做<br />\n跟本就叫唔停 因為無人知邊個做<br />\n手足就算停 啲狗一樣破壞<br />\n最終只會分化我地 <br />\n<br />\n記住<br />\n「<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你覺得呢個行動岩就去做 我地無教條主義</span></span>」"},{"pid":"b6a741d99f37f130ab84e2bf6541aa9a63e5b5f2","tid":1631520,"uid":130079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:42:14.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"291c7a2e7b386e53ef96f63fb6618c3d9b4ffedb","tid":1631520,"uid":56857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:43:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你覺得岩就去做 我地無教條主義</span></span>"},{"pid":"6898322167095b2edfa790c1277dbc72b14c1a76","tid":1631520,"uid":56857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:43:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你覺得岩就去做 我地無教條主義</span></span>"},{"pid":"300114deb6b3fab70c49de85addfb8a85cddf662","tid":1631520,"uid":56857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:44:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你覺得岩就去做 我地無教條主義</span></span>"},{"pid":"10166c44481c547c583137d826b25ffdadc2ba13","tid":1631520,"uid":56857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:44:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你覺得岩就去做 我地無教條主義</span></span>"},{"pid":"c59e3fca1c1a1c67658f07d15c3f7a93f467f9de","tid":1631520,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:44:36.000Z","msg":"大家知唔知道宜家外國人點諗勇武<br />\n勇武要大家backup 啊！<br />\n記唔記得當初應承過<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>核彈都唔割</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n正式宣布：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">文宣洗地</span></strong></span>開始［行動po求置頂］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630198\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630198</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b973a7d3e8371a5e5952e8428c7bf30f2e4d3f10","tid":1631520,"uid":56857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:44:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你覺得岩就去做 我地無教條主義</span></span>"},{"pid":"3fcb7e3225b7