red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你覺得岩就去做 我地無教條主義</span></span>"},{"pid":"4abdcd07c4eaf4e1ae51ac61a38f4421209b7e4d","tid":1631520,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:47:11.000Z","msg":"一定唔割<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">「極重要」《三份英國外交及國會報告》：當代及後世香港抗爭者之啟示</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631132\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631132</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"33e074324a052afd8bbd5c169f195d19af33913c","tid":1631520,"uid":8532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:47:14.000Z","msg":"點樣都唔會割<br />\n講左好多次<br />\n<br />\n大家要團結"},{"pid":"5c4a7c1b75678f5dd1b16a1eabef4c159913315f","tid":1631520,"uid":56857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:48:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你覺得岩就去做 我地無教條主義</span></span>"},{"pid":"0f2fe1faeb15570c9275fc36463752ddfc5ab887","tid":1631520,"uid":56857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33e074324a052afd8bbd5c169f195d19af33913c","tid":1631520,"uid":8532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:47:14.000Z","msg":"點樣都唔會割<br />\n講左好多次<br />\n<br />\n大家要團結"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:49:04.000Z","msg":"無錯"},{"pid":"393fa25f3cf175f1ab8cc982815f51193923e133","tid":1631520,"uid":56857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4abdcd07c4eaf4e1ae51ac61a38f4421209b7e4d","tid":1631520,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:47:11.000Z","msg":"一定唔割<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">「極重要」《三份英國外交及國會報告》：當代及後世香港抗爭者之啟示</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631132\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631132</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:49:28.000Z","msg":"唔割唔責備"},{"pid":"1cb6b807f00aa04be412f4d5df7507efd216ea94","tid":1631520,"uid":261386,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:50:47.000Z","msg":"永不割蓆，大家要明白點解黑警咁放肆，777咁無賴<br />\n就係呢班仆街都死不割蓆之餘，仲不停做臥底嫁禍俾我哋。<br />\n<br />\n所以大家記住唔可以被分化。<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"aad56e939d4292b0858f68d25972e4c23b7bb506","tid":1631520,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:55:59.000Z","msg":"不分不割"},{"pid":"a58e922c98246ff36cba47f052db7be7abf4a058","tid":1631520,"uid":35228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:57:53.000Z","msg":"冇錯<br />\n就好似黑警咁<br />\n就算幾錯都好<br />\n我地對外都會包容<br />\n但內部檢討<br />\n不完美，可接受，有改善空間<br />\n呢一句好撚中ＰＯＩＮＴ<br />\n不得不承認黑警呢一點我地需要學"},{"pid":"436ff5cd2abb57ff4316d9853a416d2d4ab93686","tid":1631520,"uid":8532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:58:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化 不割蓆 不完美 可改善</span></strong></span>"}]}